\c 9
\s USawuli ukhethwa ukuthi abe yinkosi
\p
\v 1 Kwakukhona-ke indoda yakoBhenjamini obizo layo linguKishi, indodana kaAbiyeli, indodana kaZerori, indodana kaBekorathi, indodana kaAfiya, umBhenjamini, iqhawe elilamandla\x + 14.51. 1 Lan. 8.33. 9.39.\x*.
\v 2 Njalo yayilendodana, obizo layo lalinguSawuli, ijaha elihle; kwakungelamuntu omuhle kulalo phakathi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 8.16.\x*; kusukela emahlombe alo kusiya phezulu lalilide kulabo bonke abantu\x + 10.23.\x*.
\v 3 Obabhemikazi bakaKishi, uyise kaSawuli, balahleka-ke. Ngakho uKishi wathi kuSawuli indodana yakhe: Ake uthathe enye yezinceku lawe, usukume uhambe uyedinga obabhemikazi.
\v 4 Wasedabula intaba zakoEfrayimi\x + Josh. 24.33.\x*, wadabula ilizwe leShalisha\x + 2 Kho. 4.42.\x*, kodwa kababatholanga. Basebedabula ilizwe leShalima\x + 13.17.\x*, kodwa babengekho. Basebedabula ilizwe lakoBhenjamini, kodwa kababatholanga.
\v 5 Bona sebefikile elizweni leZufi\x + 9.11,14. 1.1.\x*, uSawuli wathi encekwini yakhe eyayilaye: Woza sibuyele, hlezi ubaba ayekele obabhemikazi abesenqinekela thina\x + 10.2. Mat. 6.27,31,34. 10.19. Luka 12.11,22,25,26.\x*.
\v 6 Yasisithi kuye: Khangela-ke, kulomuntu kaNkulunkulu kulumuzi, ungumuntu ohloniphekayo\x + Hlu. 13.6.\x*; konke akutshoyo kuyenzeka sibili. Khathesi asiye khona; mhlawumbe angasitshela indlela esizahamba ngayo\x + 3.19.\x*.
\v 7 USawuli wasesithi encekwini yakhe: Kodwa khangela, uba sisiya, sizamphathelani lowomuntu\x + 1 Kho. 14.3. 2 Kho. 4.42. 8.8.\x*? Ngoba isinkwa kasisekho ezitsheni zethu; futhi kakulasipho sokusa emuntwini kaNkulunkulu. Silani\x + Hlu. 13.6.\x*?
\v 8 Inceku yasibuya yamphendula uSawuli yathi: Khangela, kutholakala esandleni sami ingxenye yesine \w yeshekeli\w** lesiliva; ngizamnika yona lowomuntu kaNkulunkulu ukuze asitshele indlela yethu.
\v 9 (Endulo koIsrayeli lapho umuntu esiyabuza kuNkulunkulu\x + Gen. 25.22.\x*, wayesitsho kanje: Woza siye kumboni; ngoba lo ongumprofethi lamuhla kuqala wayebizwa \add ngokuthi\add* ngumboni\x + 2 Sam. 15.27. 1 Lan. 26.28. 2 Lan. 16.7,10. Isa. 30.10.\x*.)
\v 10 USawuli wasesithi encekwini yakhe: Lihle ilizwi lakho; woza sihambe. Basebesiya emzini lapho okwakukhona lowomuntu kaNkulunkulu.
\p
\v 11 Besenyuka ngomqanso womuzi, bona bafica amantombazana ephuma ukuyakukha amanzi, bathi kuwo: Umboni ulapha yini\x + Gen. 24.11.\x*?
\v 12 Asebaphendula athi: Ukhona; khangelani, uphambi kwenu. Phangisani khathesi; ngoba ufike lamuhla emzini, ngoba abantu balomhlatshelo lamuhla endaweni ephakemeyo\x + 10.5. 1 Kho. 3.2-4.\x*.
\v 13 Ekungeneni kwenu emzini, lizahle limthole engakenyukeli endaweni ephakemeyo ukuyakudla\x + 10.5. 1 Kho. 3.2-4.\x*; ngoba abantu kabayikudla aze afike, ngoba nguye obusisa umhlatshelo, emva kwalokho abanxusiweyo badle. Ngakho-ke yenyukani, ngoba yena, phose ngalesisikhathi, lizamthola.
\v 14 Basebesenyukela emzini; besangena phakathi komuzi, khangela, uSamuweli waphuma ukubahlangabeza ukwenyukela endaweni ephakemeyo.
\p
\v 15 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasibonakalisa \add e\add*ndleb\add eni\add* kaSamuweli ngosuku phambi kokufika kukaSawuli\x + 15.1. Seb. 13.21.\x*, isithi:
\v 16 Kusasa phose ngalesisikhathi ngizathuma kuwe umuntu ovela elizweni lakoBhenjamini; futhi umgcobe abe ngumbusi phezu kwabantu bami uIsrayeli, ukuze asindise abantu bami esandleni samaFilisti\x + 10.1.\x*, ngoba ngibonile abantu bami, ngoba ukukhala kwabo kufikile kimi\x + Eks. 2.25. 3.7,9.\x*.
\v 17 Kwathi uSamuweli ebona uSawuli, iN\nd kosi\nd* yamphendula\x + Hlu. 18.14. Mat. 11.25.\x*: Khangela, umuntu ebengikhuluma ngaye kuwe. Lo uzabusa phezu kwabantu bami\x + 16.12.\x*.
\v 18 USawuli wasesondela kuSamuweli phakathi kwesango wathi: Akungitshele, ingaphi lapha indlu yomboni?
\v 19 USamuweli wasemphendula uSawuli wathi: Yimi umboni; yenyuka phambi kwami uye endaweni ephakemeyo, ngoba lamuhla uzakudla lami; lekuseni ngizakuyekela uhambe, ngikutshele konke okusenhliziyweni yakho.
\v 20 Lamayelana labobabhemikazi bakho asebelensuku ezintathu belahlekile, ungafaki inhliziyo yakho kubo, ngoba sebetholiwe\x + 9.3.\x*. Kodwa zikubani iziloyiso zonke zikaIsrayeli? Kazikho kuwe yini lendlini yonke kayihlo?
\v 21 USawuli wasephendula wathi: Kangisuye umBhenjamini yini, owesincinyane sezizwe zakoIsrayeli\x + Hlu. 20.46-48. 21.6. Hlab. 68.27.\x*, losendo lwethu luncinyane kulazo zonke insendo zesizwe sakoBhenjamini? Pho-ke, ukhulumelani kimi ngalindlela\x + 15.17. Hlu. 6.15.\x*?
\v 22 USamuweli wasethatha uSawuli lenceku yakhe, wabangenisa ekamelweni lokudlela\x + 2 Kho. 23.11. Jer. 35.2. 36.12.\x*, wabahlalisa endaweni engaphezulu yabanxusiweyo, ababengaphose babe ngamatshumi amathathu.
\v 23 USamuweli wasesithi kumpheki: Letha isabelo engikunike sona, engithe kuwe ngaso: Sibeke ngakuwe.
\v 24 Umpheki wasephakamisa umlenze lokwakuphezu kwawo, wakubeka phambi kukaSawuli\x + Eks. 29.22,27. Levi 7.32,33. Hez. 24.4.Gen. 43.34.\x*. \add USamuweli\add* wasesithi: Khangela, okuseleyo; kubeke phambi kwakho, dlana; ngoba bekubekelwe wena kuze kufike lesisikhathi esimisiweyo, \add njengoba\add* ngitshilo: Nginxuse abantu. USawuli wasesidla loSamuweli ngalolosuku.
\p
\v 25 Sebehlile endaweni ephakemeyo baya emzini, wakhuluma loSawuli ephahleni\x + 2 Sam. 11.2.\x*.
\v 26 Basebevuka ngovivi; kwasekusithi phose emadabukakusa, uSamuweli wambiza uSawuli ephahleni esithi: Sukuma ukuze ngikuyekele uhambe. Wasesukuma uSawuli, baphuma bobabili, yena loSamuweli, baya phandle.
\v 27 Sebesehlela ekucineni komuzi, uSamuweli wathi kuSawuli: Tshela inceku ukuthi yedlule phambi kwethu (yasisedlula), kodwa wena mana okwakhathesi, ukuthi ngikuzwise ilizwi likaNkulunkulu.